ygData.messageBody:
I took the advice of a fellow monk on this mailing list. I was from
Freeport and at level 6 I went west to Qeynos (solo through HighHold without
Sow or Invis ;) hehe ) and found the frogloks in the Qeynos Aqueducts. The
frogloks are a little tough at level 6, but you can find someone else to
help you out. I got most of what i wanted in the first night there, and
helped out a lower level monk and finished my collection of netted on the
2nd night.

Right now I am level 12 and looking for players selling mesh in the freeport
area once again, but i havent found anyone yet. In a couple of levels maybe
I will head to Guk. Also, I picked up a LJ hide vest or whatever it was
called for 30pp.

Sleet
Brell Serilis
